## Available commands:

In channel:
    nancie, tweet this: some interesting stuff
    nancie, follow frankieboy

In private:
    /msg nancie allow some_other_user

## Configuration
In config.yml:

    twitter:
      login: awesome
      password: something
    irc:
      nick: awesome_not
      nickserv: nickserv_password
      channel: awesome_channel
      server: irc.freenode.net
      port: 6667
    allowed:
    - user1
    - user2
